00:10:11,567 --> 00:10:12,263
valider,

246
00:10:12,263 --> 00:10:12,913
Select,

247
00:10:12,913 --> 00:10:13,610
quitter les options,

248
00:10:13,610 --> 00:10:14,283
et voilà,

249
